    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The An-gel cried to__ her_______ that is__ full_____ of____ grace: O pure___ Vir----gin, re-joice,____ and a--gain I say,_______ re--joice; for thy Son____ hath a-ris----en__ from the grave____ on the__ third________ day. \n\nShine,______ shine,___________ O____ new__ Je-ru-------sa--lem, for the glo-ry of__ the Lord____ hath a-ris----en up--on________ thee; dance now and__ be glad, O Si----on,__ and do____ thou__ do thou__ ex---ult,__ O___ pure___ The-o-to----kos,__ in the a-ris--------ing of__ Him__ Whom thou_____ didst____ bear.__________"
    }
  }
